<span id="freeTextContainer11798775815900192567">Here&apos;s an idea - what if we read Christmas books ANY time of the year, and not just at Christmastime? Around Christmas there is an emphasis on gratitude, charity, kindness, and love, which is wonderful, but there&apos;s no reason to focus on those things only in December. This book helped to remind me how much I truly have to be grateful for. Wonderful story.</span>
